'''肯尼迪纪念馆'''（[[希伯来语|希伯来语]]：{{Hebrew|יד קנדי}}，Yad Kennedy）位于[[以色列|以色列]][[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]附近（距离市中心11公里处），位于海拔825米的山顶，是为纪念在1963年被刺的美国第35届总统[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]而建。它高18米，形如砍伐的树桩，象征寿命减短。<ref name="nyt">{{cite web |url=http://jfk.hood.edu/Collection/White%20Materials/White%20Assassination%20Clippings%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20III/Misc%20III%20126.pdf |last=Feron |first=James |title=Warren dedicates Kennedy Memorial in Israel |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=5 July 1966 |accessdate=8 September 2012 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083341/http://jfk.hood.edu/Collection/White%20Materials/White%20Assassination%20Clippings%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20III/Misc%20III%20126.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 内部是肯尼迪铜像，周围环以51根柱子，象征美国的50个州以及首都华盛顿哥伦比亚特区<ref name="chronicle">{{cite web |url=http://pjn.library.cmu.edu/books/CALL1/CHR_1966_005_018_07011966/vol0/part0/copy0/ocr/txt/0005.txt |title=July 4 Rites Open Kennedy Shrine |work=The Jewish Chronicle |date=1 July 1966 |accessdate=3 September 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105223217/http://pjn.library.cmu.edu/books/CALL1/CHR_1966_005_018_07011966/vol0/part0/copy0/ocr/txt/0005.txt |archivedate=2013年11月5日 }}</ref>。纪念馆建于1966年，由美国犹太人社区捐赠资金。<ref name="nyt"/>

